# Infinity Technology — Modern Web POS + Technical Service Management System

Develop a modern, minimal, scalable, and production-ready web-based POS and technical service management system for a business called “Infinity Technology”, focused on:

* Technical service for phones, computers, and gaming consoles
* Sales of accessories and replacement parts
* Employee workflow management
* Inventory and repair tracking

The system must prioritize:

* Speed
* Clean architecture
* Scalability
* Excellent UI/UX
* Real-world business usability

